claim.claim-text:
2. An apparatus according to claim 1, wherein the data processor structure is further arranged for:
storing the at least one mini image file in association with an indication identifying the respective type of insert;
selecting for each of at least a number of the mail pieces, in accordance with associated ones of the insert instructions which selectively define inserts for the mail pieces, at least one of the mini image files identified by the at least one indication of the at least one type of insert which, according to the insert instructions, is intended for that mail piece;
controlling the printer for printing exclusively those representations which are defined by the at least one selected mini image file; and
controlling the at least one insert feeder station for selectively adding, in accordance with the insert instructions, inserts of the type loaded in this insert feeder station exclusively for the mail pieces for which, according to the insert instructions, inserts of this type are intended.
